========
Building
========

To build (from `pdi` directory):
`make release`

To run (from `pdi` directory):
`./build/release/pdi`

To generate graph (from `pdi` directory):
`make graph`
The result will be in `pdi/results/output.png`


============
Source Files
============

All the source files can be found in `pdi/src`.

pdi.h - contains all the business logic of the program (parsing arguments,
        managing threads, etc.)

main.c - entrypoint to the program

